nodes.text: The Dulok battleship was a canoe built by Gorneesh's tribe of Duloks on the Forest Moon of Endor. King Gorneesh intended to use the battleship to plunder the Fishing Festival of the Ewoks of Bright Tree Village and steal all their fish. However, the Ewoks Wicket Wystri Warrick, Teebo, Latara, and Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka foiled his plan when they teamed up with a colony of skibs to destroy the watercraft.
